{"tid":2197854,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國企哈藥集團收購GNC Rubio憂百萬計美國人私隱安全 促財政部檢視交易","createTime":"2020-09-11T02:31:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-13T20:01:56.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb6f3ed69c92ed7272ed0546e0269a85caa76744","tid":2197854,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:31:46.000Z","msg":"美國共和黨國會參議員魯比奧(Marco Rubio)促請財政部，檢視哈藥集團股份(600664.SH)收購美國保健品牌GNC的交易，指有關收購可能導致數以百萬計美國民眾的個人資料，流入中國政府手上。<br />\n<br />\nGNC於7月申請破產保護，其後哈藥集團提出注資3億美元，換取GNC主要資產，使其擺脫破產保護。<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧周四接受霍士新聞訪問時稱，哈藥集團是一間中國國企，如果任由其收購GNC，勢必導致數以百萬計美國民眾的個人資料流到中國政府。<br />\n<br />\n魯比奧促請財長努欽，指令外國投資委員會(CFIUS)檢視有關交易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2580229/美參議員促財政部+檢視哈藥收購GNC交易\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2580229%2F%E7%BE%8E%E5%8F%83%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E4%BF%83%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%83%A8%2B%E6%AA%A2%E8%A6%96%E5%93%88%E8%97%A5%E6%94%B6%E8%B3%BCGNC%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93&d=u5s3JLQ1HZhTjCUFZ9m1FEngG4XMVyvHznkFIzn%2BcUY%3D&h=73d88ba7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2580229/美參議員促財政部+檢視哈藥收購GNC交易</a>"},{"pid":"e6455d0fb6194256fd3212355433bc9e3511e68c","tid":2197854,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4955f0bc75a803057474aa51cad06b9e22d02a77","tid":2197854,"uid":100680,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:36:35.000Z","msg":"睇黎支那真係有決心要控制全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88f54b022009cde4a547469e519fc5d34a46fad","tid":2197854,"uid":261699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:37:13.000Z","msg":"一定要禁佢收購啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a732028af4cedc589890dc3c3a36ee63ef33ec6d","tid":2197854,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T02:47:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b992935c526cf6772877b4cdd0cd862cce8d7e7e","tid":2197854,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:03:25.000Z","msg":"本身GNC都已經比支企做左最大股東<br />\n而家玩到玻產再食埋人地<br />\n<br />\n2018年2月24日，中國大陸企業哈藥集團斥資3億美元入股GNC40.1％的股權，從而成為其單一最大股東"},{"pid":"7dca88ab6646909dd6a75f768264531525cc653b","tid":2197854,"uid":291526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"普通人唔知仲以為係外企<br />\n其實一早變晒中資<br />\n呢啲例子真係數都數唔晒"},{"pid":"de850b42fb230fce812c88b057f3da19fa536dfd","tid":2197854,"uid":358640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dca88ab6646909dd6a75f768264531525cc653b","tid":2197854,"uid":291526,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"普通人唔知仲以為係外企<br />\n其實一早變晒中資<br />\n呢啲例子真係數都數唔晒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"做個美國板 red list<br />\n等美國人知道下自己衣食住行已經被中共包圍"}]}